platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: 收到喜愛的名人為你錄製的專屬影片，是一種十分特別的體驗。無論是送禮或犒賞自己，這款 App 都能讓你或對方離心愛中的明星更近一點。

There’s something special about getting a personalized video from one of your favourite celebrities. Whether a gift for a friend or for yourself, this app makes feeling starstruck a bit more accessible.
